high_descs: Turn left, take a few steps forward, and then turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote from the table.
Turn left, take a few steps forward, and then turn left towards red pillow on the green sofa.
Place the remote on the newsletter to the right of the red pillow.
Turn around, walk towards the fireplace, turn left and walk towards the tv stand on your right.
Pick up the remote on the tv stand.
Turn left, take a few steps forward, and then turn left towards red pillow on the green sofa.
Place the remote on the newsletter to the right of the red pillow.
anns.task_desc: Place the two tv remotes to the right of the red pillow on the green sofa.

high_descs: Walk over to the fireplace, then turn left and walk up to the coffee table.
Pick up the remote off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the couch.
Put the remote in the seat of the couch on top of the newspaper.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up the fire place, turn left and walk over to the shelving unit the television is on.
Pick up the remote off of the middle shelf of the shelving unit.
Turn right and walk around the coffee table to the couch.
Put the remote on the seat of the couch behind the remote that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two remotes to the couch.

high_descs: Turn left and go between the fireplace and coffee table, then face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote controller to the left of the open laptop.
Go around the left end of the coffee table to face the center of the green sofa.
Put the controller on top of the newspaper to the right of the red pillow, parallel to the side of the seat cushion.
Turn to your left and go back around the coffee table to the red shelves to the left of the fireplace.
Get the remote controller from the shelf below the TV screen.
Turn around and retrace your path back to the center of the green sofa.
Place the remote controller directly in a line behind the first one, between the first controller and the back of the sofa.
anns.task_desc: Move two remote controllers to a sofa.
